des: The Flash Briefing for San Francisco 49ers fans need from Locked On 49ers. Follow your team every day with on-demand insights, news, interviews and perspective from insider Brian Peacock. Locked On 49ers is part of the Locked On Podcast Network, the #1 local daily sports podcast network. Locked On covers every NFL and NBA team with a growing list of MLB and major College teams too. To listen to the daily podcast, just ask Alexa to play the Locked On 49ers podcast. Get Locked On and follow “YOUR TEAM. EVERY DAY”.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
